title: [Ilynov Manor, Courtyard]
description: Moonlight shines over a stone wall, casting the tall, overgrown hedge lining a stately manor's courtyard into deep shadow.  A leaf-strewn brick path stretches between a rusty iron gate and the steps leading to the manor's doors.  Barely distinguishable in the blackness under the boughs of an enormous weeping willow sits a wrought iron bench.
location: Ilynov Manor, inside the elven fortress of Ta'Vaalor
